      "writtenOn": "2024-04-29T14:01:05Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I think we should just let the user provide both the provider and algorithm if they want to use OVN. That is the current case with the Heat driver, and also the current case with Octavia.\n\nI am aiming to get the driver as thin as possible, so we do not have to maintain this code when upstream changes (e.g. ovn-octavia supporting other algo, or Octavia setting this for us automagically)",
      "revId": "63d281e6749a07fe636603ae53e0e4f0e5fbfc9c",
      "serverId": "4a232e18-c5a9-48ee-94c0-e04e7cca6543"
    },
    {
